## 1. Required API keys — gather these before MCP installs

You will need:

| Key | Where to get | Used by |
|---|---|---|
| `PERPLEXITY_API_KEY` | https://www.perplexity.ai/settings/api | Perplexity MCP |
| `FIRECRAWL_API_KEY` | https://www.firecrawl.dev/app (sign in → API Keys) | Firecrawl MCP |
| `GLIF_API_TOKEN` | https://glif.app/settings/api-tokens | Glif MCP |
| Higgsfield | OAuth/login flow on first call | Higgsfield MCP (HTTP transport — no token needed for install) |

The `claude mcp add` commands below use `REPLACE_*` placeholders. Substitute your real keys when you run them.

**Do not paste your keys back into this chat.** They sit in your terminal history and `claude mcp` config only.

