## 7. Troubleshooting

**`claude mcp add` says command not found.**
Claude Code CLI is not on your PATH. Reinstall from https://docs.claude.com/en/docs/claude-code/install or check `where claude` in PowerShell.

**Playwright MCP fails to launch a browser.**
Run `npm run test:e2e:install` once at the project root to grab Chromium with dependencies.

**Higgsfield doesn't authenticate.**
The HTTP transport opens a browser window the first time. Make sure you complete the OAuth flow. If your default browser is locked down, try copying the auth URL from the Claude Code prompt into another browser.

**Marketplace `/plugin install` does nothing.**
You're already covered by the manual fallback at `.claude/skills/ui-ux-pro-max/SKILL.md`. Alternatively run `npm install -g uipro-cli && uipro init --ai claude --global` to install the full skill at the user level.

**`claude mcp list` shows nothing after install.**
Restart Claude Code. MCP config is read at session start.

